data.description: Charming home with a fresh appeal, featuring a new garage door, updated appliances, and a newly installed kitchen floor. The original hardwood floors have been beautifully restained, while the living room boasts new drywall. Located in a kid-friendly neighborhood, this property is conveniently close to downtown Detroit and surrounded by great restaurants and bars. Ideal for those seeking modern comforts in a welcoming community.
